{"article_id":"UyzENqPk0o3sYf1f","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republicans seem to be humoring a gun control proposal","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to ban \" bump stocks \" - a device","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"the Las Vegas shooter likely used","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to make his semiautomatic weapon function as a fully automatic one .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"In the wake of the tragic mass shooting in Las Vegas ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"which left 59 dead and injured hundreds more ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Democrats and Republicans in both the House and Senate have proposed banning bump stocks .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Police found 12 bump stock devices in the hotel room","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"the Nevada gunman shot from ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"an explanation for the rapid gunfire at the incident .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"If the Republican-led Congress does decide to implement some kind of gun reform in response to the shooting","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"- considered the deadliest in modern US history -","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"this narrow restriction of bump stock sales appears to be the best bet .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"The push has come from Democrats , like Dianne Feinstein","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"in the Senate and in the House , a bipartisan effort from Carlos Curbelo","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"( R-FL )","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and Seth Moulton","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"( D-MA ) ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"but Republicans at large have signaled","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"they are open to similar legislation .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"\" Fully automatic weapons have been banned for a long time , \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan said .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"\" Apparently this allows you to take a semiautomatic","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and turn it into a fully automatic ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"so clearly that 's something","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"we need to look into . ''","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"But there are already signs","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"that this push could be all talk .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"The National Rifle Association ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"which orginally said","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"bump stocks should be \" subject to additional regulations , \"","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"is now saying","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"any action should come from the Trump administration","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"- not from Congress -","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"a distinction","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that will likely muddy hopes of any action on Capitol Hill .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"With each mass shooting , Congress reignites a longstanding debate on gun control .","depth":3},{"id":38,"text":"But it ' s largely one","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"that fizzles out in time ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"resulting in little to no legislative changes .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"This time Democrats might have found the narrowest version of gun control legislation","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"that could conceivably bring Republicans on board .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"If this doesn ' t work ,","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"it shows just how unlikely any gun reform legislation is under a Republican-led Congress .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"Already top congressional Republicans have expressed interest","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"in at least considering the ban","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"- which is more attention","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"than most gun control proposals get from the GOP .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"Majority Whip Sen. John Cornyn said","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"it would be \" worthwhile \" to have a hearing on the legislation ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"the devices are \" certainly something","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that ' s got my attention","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"and I think","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"we ought to get to the bottom of it. \"","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"The third-ranking Republican senator , North Dakota ' s John Thune , also said","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"\" it ' s something","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"we ought to look into . \"","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"\" It looks to me that these kits","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that turn these things into automatic weapons","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"is a place","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"you could really get some bipartisan support , \"","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Oklahoma Rep. Tom Cole , a top Republican in the House , told .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Even some of the most conservative Congress members have said","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"it ' s something","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"they could consider .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Rep. Joe Barton","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"( R-TX ) ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"who said","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"there is little wiggle room in the Second Amendment ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"he ' d look at a bump stock ban ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"and Rep. Mark Meadows","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"( R-NC ) ,","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"who chairs the ultraconservative House Freedom Caucus ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"he could be for it .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"On its own , the bump stock ban seems narrow enough","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"that Republicans can explain supporting it :","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Automatic weapons are mostly banned in the United States ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"and this device is essentially a loophole to that regulation .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" The only reason","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"you would need that kind of capability","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"I believe","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"is to kill a lot of people very fast , \"","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Rep. Tom Rooney","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"( R-FL )","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"said on CNN .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"\" And so ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"when somebody tries to equate that to me holding a handgun","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"when I 'm driving to the movies or to a mall with my kids for protection ,","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"I just do n't buy it .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"I 'm not buying it . \"","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"But public support for this kind of legislation spikes in the immediate aftermath of a mass shooting","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"- an energy","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"that eventually fizzles out in the following months ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"making an already low-priority issue for Republican members even less pressing .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"And already many top Republicans ,","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"including Thune and Cornyn ,","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"are saying","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"they need to know more .","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"The line from congressional Republicans is that","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"despite most of them being gun owners ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"they had never heard of bump stocks before the Las Vegas shooting .","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"House Majority Whip Rep. Steve Scalise","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"( R-LA ) ,","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"who just returned to Congress","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"after being critically injured at a mass shooting","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"targeting congressional Republicans in the summer ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"poured some cold water on the energy behind the effort .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"\" I do think","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"it 's a little bit early for people to say","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"they know what to do","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"to fix this problem , \"","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"he told NBC News ' s Meet the Press with Chuck Todd .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"\" If you talk to anybody about a week ago ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"most people ,","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"including myself ,","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"didn ' t even know","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"what a bump stock was . \"","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"\" There are people","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"that want to rush to judgment , \"","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"he continued .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"\" They 've got a bill","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"written already . \"","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"To be clear ,","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"Feinstein ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"who is sponsoring the Senate bill ,","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"had raised the issue of bump stocks in 2013","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"- to no avail .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Despite Republicans pleading ignorance ,","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"this isn ' t the first time","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"a ban on bump stocks has been brought up in Congress .","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"Feinstein had raised concern about bump stocks in Congress ,","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"bringing up a similar but more sweeping restriction in 2013","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"that proposed banning all semiautomatic weapons","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"that could accept a \" military feature \" like a detachable stock .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"At the time , the bill faced fierce opposition","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"even among Democratic senators ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"including West Virginia ' s Joe Manchin .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"Now ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"as awareness around mass shootings and gun violence rises again ,","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"Feinstein ' s proposed ban is much narrower :","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"on the bump stocks themselves .","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"It ' s already seen some opposition from gun lobby groups like Gun Owners of America ,","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"which said","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"bump stocks should be available","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"\" to help gun owners with disabilities fire their weapons . \"","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"The NRA originally seemed more open .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"But they drew an important line :","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"They don ' t want this restriction written into law .","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"\" The NRA believes","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"that devices","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"designed","depth":16},{"id":155,"text":"to allow semi-automatic rifles to function like fully-automatic rifles","depth":16},{"id":156,"text":"should be subject to additional regulations , \"","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"the organization said in a statement .","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"But in a twist , it called on Trump ' s administration","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"- the Bureau of Alcohol , Tobacco , Firearms , and Explosives -","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"to review a ban on the devices .","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"In other words , the NRA is suggesting taking the matter out of Congress ' s hands .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"But in the past , ATF has said","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"it does not have purview over attachable devices like bump stocks -","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"calling on Congress to authorize any kind of ban .","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"\" If we could legislate morality ,","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"we would have done it long ago , \"","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"Wayne LaPierre , NRA executive , said on CBS ' s \" Face the Nation \" on Sunday ,","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"repeating a now time-old excuse from Republicans ,","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"that there ' s nothing","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"Congress can actually do on gun laws","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"to stop mass shootings .","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"This kind of confusion could lead to more delays","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"and ultimately allow the gun control debate to fizzle out ,","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"as it has many times in the past .","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"\" I am sure","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"there will be some debate on it ,","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"and then we will go down the road","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"and something else will happen","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"and it will get in the background again , \"","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"Rep. Roger Williams","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"( R-TX )","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"said on whether Congress would actually address gun laws .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":365,"left":227,"right":364,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":219,"right":226,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":195,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":192,"right":194,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":192,"left":186,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":0,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":1,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":188,"right":190,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":187,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":187,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":189,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":189,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":193,"right":12,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":193,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":208,"right":217,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":200,"right":207,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{